    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward value for the right buyer. Best suited for someone seeking affordable transportation, a starter project, or a practical spare vehicle, it presents an accessible entry point without the premium price tag. An honest opportunity to own at a low cost, with room for the next owner to make it their own.",
