    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly ride with plenty of potential. It\u2019s not a showroom car, but it starts, moves, and could be a great option for someone looking for cheap transportation, a project, or a handy extra vehicle. If you\u2019re after something affordable and straightforward, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Turn-key project with strong bones and plenty of upside. Runs, drives, and has the kind of proven, mechanical simplicity enthusiasts look for when they want something they can sort and enjoy without chasing overly complex electronics. Engine pulls cleanly, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels usable as a daily beater, weekend toy, or budget build platform. It is not a show car and does have cosmetic wear, age-related blemishes, and needs TLC, but the fundamentals make it a compelling value for someone who understands what these are and what they can become. Priced to move for a buyer who wants an honest car with potential.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Honest poor-condition driver with wear, flaws, and plenty of life for the right buyer. Priced to move fast.",
