      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with tons of personality, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn charm that makes it feel like the start of your next great project. It\u2019s the perfect candidate for someone who sees potential where others see patina\u2014a budget-friendly ride for weekend tinkering, a creative build, or simply dependable transportation with character. If you\u2019ve been looking for an affordable entry point into ownership and don\u2019t mind giving it a little love, this one offers a lot of story for the money.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Straightforward, affordable transportation offered with complete honesty. This vehicle shows its age and is best suited for a buyer looking for dependable basic mobility, a work commuter, or a practical project. A great opportunity to get into a budget-friendly vehicle from a seller focused on clear, professional representation and fair value.",
