      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with strong enthusiast upside. Starts, runs, and offers a solid mechanical foundation for someone who appreciates an honest car with usable bones. The powertrain feels eager, the chassis is straightforward, and it presents as a great candidate for continued sorting, weekend wrenching, or budget fun. Not a showroom piece, but a compelling platform with character, serviceable hardware, and the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes ownership approachable. If you want an affordable entry point with real potential, this one is worth a look.",
